      "_id": "card_meta_app_review_2026_03_22",
      "columnId": "backlog",
      "title": "Submit Meta App Review for Instagram DM automation",
      "description": "Required to message real Instagram commenters via official API. Single-business apps have a streamlined process.\n\nContext: /Users/openclaw/handoffs/2026-03-22-instagram-automation-direction.md\n\nWhat to do:\n1. Go to developers.facebook.com/apps/1967892840469594\n2. Go to App Review → Request permissions\n3. Request: instagram_business_manage_messages + instagram_business_manage_comments\n4. Record a 2-min screencast showing the flow (comment keyword → DM → email capture → link sent)\n5. Submit — single-business apps typically approved in 2-7 days\n\nOnce approved: build the full custom system (Vercel webhook + Supabase) and cancel ManyChat.\n\nApp already created: OpenIGClaw-IG (ID: 1967892840469594, Secret in .env)",
      "order": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "updatedAt": 1742601600000
    },
    {
      "_id": "card_dr_alla_website_775776",
      "columnId": "claude-code",
      "title": "Set up Dr Alla website",
      "description": "1. Create project at ~/.openclaw/workspace/projects/dr-alla/ (CONTEXT.md, credentials)\n2. Save login credentials to LastPass under \"Dr Alla Website\"\n3. Save credentials to project CONTEXT.md\n4. Add Dr Alla to SEO dropdown in MC SEO page\n5. Build programmatic access via agent-browser so we can interact with the site\n6. Verify login works and document CLI commands for future automation\n\nWaiting on: Website URL + login credentials from Joe.",
