      "priority": "medium",
      "tags": [
        "seo",
        "client"
      ],
      "createdAt": 1774148942822
    },
    {
      "_id": "card_ig_automation_2026_03_22",
      "columnId": "backlog",
      "title": "Set up Meta App for Instagram comment automation (replaces ManyChat)",
      "description": "One-time setup (~20 min) to enable fully automated comment→DM→email capture without ManyChat.\n\n**Instructions: /Users/openclaw/handoffs/2026-03-22-instagram-automation-direction.md**\n\nWhat to do:\n1. Go to developers.facebook.com\n2. Create new app → type: Business\n3. Add product: Instagram\n4. Connect instagram account: joe.che.official\n5. Generate User Access Token with scopes:\n   - instagram_business_basic\n   - instagram_business_manage_comments\n   - instagram_business_manage_messages\n6. Paste into ~/.openclaw/workspace/.env:\n   META_APP_ID=...\n   META_APP_SECRET=...\n   META_IG_ACCESS_TOKEN=...\n   META_IG_ACCOUNT_ID=...\n\nOnce done, tell Claude to build the Vercel webhook handler + Supabase schema.\n\nContext: ManyChat is being dropped (/mo, no email export, no API for cloning flows). Replacing with official Instagram Graph API + Vercel + Supabase. Zero manual steps per giveaway after setup.",
      "order": 1,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "updatedAt": 1742601600000
    },
    {
      "_id": "8b519759-3397-4b21-bdbe-1d4d4f7d0d23",
      "columnId": "claude-code",
      "title": "Research ManyChat API for OpenClaw integration",
      "description": "The PDF \"Setter with Claude @TheGrowthCeo\" shows ManyChat has a built-in Claude integration (UI-based). Research whether ManyChat has a REST API that OpenClaw can call programmatically to:\n- Send/receive Instagram DMs\n- Trigger automations\n- Manage contacts/flows\nCheck: https://manychat.com/api (ManyChat API docs). Determine if we can build an OpenClaw agent that uses ManyChat as the Instagram DM layer with Claude doing the AI responses, without going through the ManyChat UI.",
      "order": 6,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-15T16:12:38.492827Z",
      "updatedAt": 1773800783966
    },
    {
      "_id": "card_remotion_1773486995684",
      "title": "Remotion: Install, Create Agent, Research Uses",
      "description": "1. Install Remotion\n2. Create a Remotion agent\n3. Research the best ways to use it for Masterminds HQ\n\n## Key Opportunities for Masterminds HQ:\n\n**Personalized Video Creation**\n- Custom video invites for mastermind cohorts\n- Personalized testimonial videos\n- Event highlight reels for participants\n\n**Real-Time Data-Driven Videos**\n- Results showcase videos (before/after metrics)\n- Progress tracking videos\n- Live performance updates\n\n**Automated Content Generation at Scale**\n- Batch personalized videos for all members\n- Automated testimonial compilations\n- Marketing video generation\n\n**Marketing & Promotional Videos**\n- Landing page videos\n- Social media promotional content\n- Custom video editor for client deliverables\n\n## Business Models:\n- SaaS video editor platforms\n- Agency services (personalized video production)\n- White-label solutions\n- Event video automation services\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-14 22:09)\nThe background render test completed successfully too — the agent CLI, templates, job tracking, MC page, and API are all working end-to-end.",
