    {
      "_id": "card_1772902811234",
      "title": "[Passive Income] ChatGPT/Claude Prompt Packs for Professionals",
      "description": "1. Research top-selling prompt packs on Gumroad (scrape categories, prices, reviews)\n2. Create 10 profession-specific prompt packs:\n   - Real estate agents (listing descriptions, client emails, market analysis)\n   - Lawyers (contract review, legal research, client communication)\n   - Marketers (ad copy, email sequences, social media calendars)\n   - Teachers (lesson plans, rubrics, parent communications)\n   - Small business owners (business plans, financial analysis, hiring)\n   - Content creators (video scripts, blog outlines, SEO)\n   - HR professionals (job descriptions, interview questions, onboarding)\n   - Accountants (client reports, tax explanations, advisory letters)\n   - Freelancers (proposals, invoicing, client management)\n   - Consultants (slide decks, deliverables, engagement letters)\n3. Each pack: 50-100 prompts, tested with Claude, formatted as beautiful PDF + raw text file\n4. Create Gumroad listings with preview images and descriptions\n5. Build Mission Control dashboard at /app/prompt-packs:\n   - Sales per pack, total revenue, conversion rates\n   - Customer feedback tracker\n   - Ideas for new packs based on search trends\n6. Pricing: $9 per pack, $39 bundle of 5, $69 all-access\n\n---\nCONTEXT\n- Startup budget: $0\n- Manual steps (user must do): Upload to Gumroad/Etsy, share in relevant communities\n- Source idea: idea_1709856005_gum01\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-08 07:31)\nAll 4 background agents confirmed complete. The entire Prompt Packs task is finished — 10 packs with content, PDFs, previews, Gumroad listings, and MC dashboard all in place.",
