    {
      "_id": "card_1772902964730",
      "title": "[Passive Income] Print-on-Demand Design Generator",
      "description": "1. Research trending niches on Redbubble/TeePublic (use their trending/popular pages)\n2. Generate 100+ text-based designs:\n   - Profession humor (\"I'm a [job], what's your superpower?\")\n   - Hobby/interest slogans (\"But first, coffee\" style)\n   - Seasonal/trending topics\n   - Niche community inside jokes \n- Focus on AI geeks, Openclaw geeks, Claude code geeks to start with. Look for trending topics and find missing texts. \n3. For each design:\n   - Claude generates the text/concept\n   - Create simple SVG or PNG designs (text + basic shapes)\n   - Write optimized title, description, tags for marketplace SEO\n4. Upload to Redbubble, TeePublic, and Merch by Amazon\n5. Build Mission Control dashboard at /app/pod-designs:\n   - Designs uploaded per platform\n   - Views, favorites, sales per design\n   - Revenue by platform\n   - Trending niches to target next\n6. Cron: weekly trending niche research, monthly sales report\n\n---\nCONTEXT\n- Startup budget: $0\n- Manual steps (user must do): Create accounts on POD platforms, upload designs (can batch upload), choose product types\n- Source idea: idea_1709856015_print01\n\n---\n**Task Executor Failed** (2026-03-08 03:04, exit: 1)\nTask timed out after 2 hours",
