      "completedAt": 1773504892476
    },
    {
      "title": "Set Up Airtable Agent + Mission Control Integration",
      "description": "## Goal\nConnect to the Airtable account (newyork1@gmail.com) and build a reusable Airtable agent + Mission Control dashboard.\n\n## Steps\n1. Retrieve Airtable credentials from LastPass (newyork1@gmail.com account)\n2. Generate/locate Airtable Personal Access Token (PAT)\n3. Create agent at ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/airtable/\n   - CLI: node ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/airtable/src/index.js <command>\n   - Commands: list-bases, list-tables, read, create-record, update-record, search\n   - Store credentials in .env as AIRTABLE_API_KEY\n4. Register in agent-registry.json + create status.json\n5. Build MC page at /app/airtable (connected bases, table browser, recent records, quick search)\n6. Add to MC sidebar + wire up /api/airtable route\n7. Rebuild MC + verify page loads (full restart protocol)\n\n## Notes\n- Account: newyork1@gmail.com, password in LastPass\n- Follow agent-creation-checklist.md (9 steps)\n- MUST follow MC restart protocol after any MC changes",
      "labels": [
        "agent",
        "integration",
        "airtable",
        "mission-control"
      ],
      "priority": "High",
      "column": "done",
      "order": 15,
      "_id": "card_1773368596214",
