      "completedAt": 1773372463300
    },
    {
      "title": "Build CashClaw Agent (Autonomous Freelancing Income)",
      "description": "## Goal\nDeploy CashClaw as an autonomous income agent -- finds work, delivers services, collects Stripe payments with zero manual intervention.\n\n## Research Summary\n- Repo: https://github.com/ertugrulakben/cashclaw (active, legitimate)\n- How it works: Define services as SKILL.md files (pricing, delivery, I/O specs). Agent finds work on HYRVEai marketplace or direct clients, delivers, collects via Stripe.\n- Pre-built skills: SEO auditing, content writing, lead generation, WhatsApp management, social media management, invoicing\n- Fees: 0% direct clients, 15% marketplace (HYRVEai)\n- Stripe: Direct integration with existing setup\n- Custom skills possible: can build mastermind/consulting skill files\n- NOTE: CashClaw Protocol at cashclaw.org is a DIFFERENT project (DeFi on Base) -- unrelated\n\n## Steps\n\n### 1. Guard Dog Scan (MANDATORY BEFORE INSTALL)\n- Run guard dog dep scan on the repo before cloning anything\n- Command: node ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/guard-dog/bin/scan-deps.js --repo https://github.com/ertugrulakben/cashclaw\n- Also run: ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/guard-dog/bin/cron-nightly-scan.sh before install\n- Do NOT proceed if guard dog flags anything critical\n\n### 2. Sign Up for HYRVEai Marketplace\n- Create account at HYRVEai marketplace (use newyork1@gmail.com)\n- Save credentials to LastPass IMMEDIATELY: site = \"HYRVEai / CashClaw\", username = newyork1@gmail.com\n- Save any CashClaw API keys/tokens to LastPass AND to ~/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n\n### 3. Clone & Install\n- Clone: git clone https://github.com/ertugrulakben/cashclaw ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/cashclaw\n- Install deps, review config\n- Connect to existing Stripe account (keys already in .env)\n\n### 4. Start with Low-Friction Skills\n- Enable SEO auditor skill first (complements mastermind SEO work)\n- Enable content writer skill\n- WhatsApp manager skill (complements wacli setup)\n\n### 5. Build Custom Mastermind Skill\n- Create SKILL.md for mastermind consulting/automation audits\n- Price: $150-500 per engagement, direct client mode (0% fee)\n\n### 6. Register as Agent (agent-creation-checklist.md, 9 steps)\n- Add to agent-registry.json\n- Create status.json\n- MC page at /app/cashclaw (active jobs, earnings, skill performance)\n- Add to MC sidebar + /api/cashclaw route\n\n### 7. MC Restart Protocol (MANDATORY after any MC changes)\n- Unload plist -> pkill next -> rm -rf .next -> reload -> curl localhost:3000/app/cashclaw\n\n## Notes\n- newyork1@gmail.com for signup, password in LastPass BEFORE any account actions\n- Guard dog scan is non-negotiable BEFORE install\n- Prioritize direct client channel (0% fee vs 15% marketplace)",
      "labels": [
        "agent",
        "passive-income",
        "cashclaw",
        "mission-control"
      ],
      "priority": "High",
      "column": "backlog",
      "order": 2,
