      "description": "Share the PostPilot landing page with 3 mastermind members who have dead/neglected blogs.\n\nLanding page: https://postpilot-landing-nine.vercel.app\n\nMessage template:\n\"I built something that writes your blog every day, automatically — SEO'd, with images, published to your site. Take a look: [URL]. I'm doing free setups for the first few people who want to try it.\"\n\nFastest path to first $49-$149 MRR. One sale = proof of concept.",
