      "description": "Add yourself or a test client with a real WordPress or Ghost site, then run a full generation.\n\n```bash\n# Add test client\nnode ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/postpilot/src/index.js client-add \\\n  --name 'Test Client' --email test@example.com \\\n  --tier starter --platform wordpress\n\n# Generate a post\nnode ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/postpilot/src/index.js generate <clientId>\n```\n\nVerify: post published with hero image, SEO meta tags, and JSON-LD schema.",
