      "description": "Write 3-email sequence sent after client pays $100:\n\n1. **Confirmation** — payment received, TidyCal link to book the call, what to expect\n2. **Pre-call prep** — ask them to gather: brand voice examples, competitors, top keywords, CMS login info\n3. **Post-call** — welcome to PostPilot, first post date, how to give feedback\n\nCurrently no automated emails exist. Can be sent manually or via ConvertKit/Beehiiv once written.",
