    {
      "title": "Set Up Wix Mastermind Recordings Page and put CMS On it",
      "description": " The one manual step (10 min in Wix Editor)\n\n  1. Add a new page — call it \"Recordings\" or \"All Recordings\"\n  2. Add a Repeater/Grid element → connect it to MastermindRecordings collection\n  3. For each card in the repeater, connect:\n    - Text element → title\n    - Embed element → youtubeId (use https://www.youtube.com/embed/{youtubeId})\n    - Optional text → description\n  4. Sort by sortOrder ascending\n  5. Filter where published = true\n  6. Set page permissions → Members only (or whatever plan)\n\n  Then paste that page URL as the single link inside your Wix Online Programs step.",
