    {
      "_id": "card_1773646374448",
      "column": "done",
      "title": "Wix Manual SEO Tasks — TCM & MHQ (page-by-page)",
      "description": "Open the Wix Editor to make these changes. Work page by page — do everything listed for that page before moving on, then save & publish.\n\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nTHE CONNECTION MAP — theconnectionmap.com\n─────────────────────────────────────────\nEditor URL: https://editor.wix.com/html/editor/web/renderer/edit/98f12266-a7bc-472e-93af-f5e6bc13e5b5\n\n── HOMEPAGE (/) ──\n1. H1: Click the heading \"Your guide to understanding your Relationships\" → change text style from H2 to H1\n2. Alt text: Find the small testimonial photo (123×123px) → click it → Settings gear → \"What is this image?\" → type: \"The Connection Map coaching testimonial\"\n3. Title tag: Pages & Menu → Homepage → 3-dot → SEO Basics → Title: \"The Relationship Quiz | The Connection Map\"\n4. Open Graph: Dashboard → Marketing & SEO → Social Share → set OG Title: \"The Connection Map — Understand Your Relationships\" and OG Description: same as meta description\n\n── /COURSES ──\n1. H1: Click the main page heading → change to H1\n2. Title tag: SEO Basics → change from \"COURSES\" to \"Online Courses & Programs | The Connection Map\"\n3. Alt text (4 images): Click each image → Settings gear → \"What is this image?\" → describe what's shown (e.g. \"Joe Che relationship coaching course\", \"online program for career growth\")\n\n── /CATEGORY/ALL-PRODUCTS ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n2. Alt text (12 images): Click each product/listing image → Settings gear → \"What is this image?\" → describe the product shown (e.g. \"Connection Map online course thumbnail\", \"relationship coaching program cover\")\n\n── /DREAMCAREER ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading \"Designing Your Dream Career\" → change to H1\n2. Alt text (2 images): Click each image → Settings gear → set descriptive alt text\n\n── /MENTORSHIP ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n2. Alt text (1 image): Click the image → Settings gear → \"What is this image?\" → e.g. \"Joe Che mentorship coaching session\"\n\n── /UNCOVER ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading \"Uncover Your Soul Purpose\" → change to H1\n\n── /UNBLOCKUNLOCK ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading \"Unblock & Unlock\" → change to H1\n\n── /MASTERMINDVSL ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n\n── /ABOUT ──\n1. Title tag: SEO Basics → change from \"ABOUT\" (26 chars) to \"About Joe Che | The Connection Map\"\n2. Alt text (1 image): Click the portrait/profile photo → Settings gear → \"What is this image?\" → \"Joe Che, author and relationship coach\"\n\n── /SIXSTEPS ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n2. Meta description: SEO Basics → trim the description to under 160 characters (currently 174)\n\n── /LEARN ──\n1. Alt text (5 images): Click each image → Settings gear → set descriptive alt text\n2. Meta description: SEO Basics → expand description (currently only 46 chars — add more detail)\n\n── /SOULPURPOSE ──\n1. H1 duplicate: This page has 2 H1 tags — find the secondary one and change it to H2\n2. Alt text (2 images): Click each image → Settings gear → set descriptive alt text\n\n── /HOME (separate page, may be a redirect) ──\n1. H1: Click main heading → change to H1\n2. Title tag: Change from \"HOME\" to \"Relationship Coaching Programs | The Connection Map\"\n3. Meta description: SEO Basics → add: \"Explore Joe Che's relationship coaching programs, online courses, and mentorship at The Connection Map. Build stronger connections and design your best life.\"\n4. Alt text (3 images): Click each → Settings gear → set descriptive alt text\n\n── QUIZ SUBDOMAIN (quiz.theconnectionmap.com) ──\nThis is a separate Wix site — open its editor separately.\n1. Title tag: Change from \"Connection Map\" to \"Relationship Quiz | The Connection Map\"\n2. Meta description: Add \"Take the free Connection Map Relationship Quiz to understand your relationship dynamics, identify patterns, and build stronger, more fulfilling connections.\"\n3. H1: Click main heading → change to H1\n4. Canonical URL: SEO Basics → set canonical to https://quiz.theconnectionmap.com/\n\n─────────────────────────────────\nMASTERMINDS HQ — mastermindshq.business\n─────────────────────────────────\nEditor URL: https://editor.wix.com/html/editor/web/renderer/edit/70e88030-8efa-455f-9213-751d686a9448\n\n── /MENTORSHIP ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n\n── /BLOG ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n\n── /FREE-TRAINING ──\n1. H1: Click the main heading → change to H1\n\n── /JOBS ──\n1. H1 duplicate: This page has 2 H1 tags — find the secondary one and change it to H2\n\n─────────────────────────────────\nAFTER ALL CHANGES\n─────────────────────────────────\nClick Publish in the top-right corner of the Wix Editor.\nThen tell the agent: \"Done with Wix SEO\" so the fix queue can be updated.",
      "labels": [
        "seo",
        "wix"
      ],
      "priority": "High",
      "project": "The Connection Map",
      "order": 0,
      "createdAt": 1773646374448,
      "updatedAt": 1774277450525,
      "completedAt": 1774277450525
