    {
      "title": "Research & Install Kling AI Video Generation",
      "description": "Kling is an AI video generation app. Full setup:\n\n1. Research Kling AI — capabilities, API availability, pricing\n2. Sign up for account using agent browser (Google login already active at port 9223)\n3. Get API key from dashboard\n4. Save API key to ~/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n5. Build agent at ~/.openclaw/workspace/agents/kling/\n6. Follow agent-creation-checklist.md (9 steps: folder, deps, registry, status.json, MC page, cron, inter-agent comms, docs, verification)\n7. Add to MC sidebar + Office Space\n\nNote: Use agent browser (port 9223) for signup/login — Google already logged in there.",
