      "title": "Install Claude Code tools: context mode MCP, CLI proxy API, Mirofish AI, primer.md, Superdata",
      "description": "Install and configure the following tools/plugins for Claude Code:\n\n1. **Context mode MCP** — MCP server enabling context mode for Claude Code\n2. **CLI proxy API** — Claude Code CLI proxy API\n3. **Mirofish AI** — Mirofish AI integration\n4. **primer.md** — primer.md tool/plugin\n5. **Superdata** — Superdata integration\n\nResearch each, install, configure, and verify they work within Claude Code.\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-18 09:12)\nSame thing — that was the other hung claude-primer process we killed. All three tools are installed and verified. Nothing else to do here.",
