      "title": "Install & Hook Up Mirofish AI + Polymarket Integration",
      "description": "Install Mirofish AI and get it fully operational.\n\nThen research and suggest how it can be integrated into the Polymarket Trader agent to enhance trading decisions.\n\n**Tasks:**\n1. Research what Mirofish AI is and how to install it\n2. Install and configure it (MCP server, CLI, or whatever format it takes)\n3. Verify it works end-to-end\n4. Analyze the Polymarket Trading agent at ~/.openclaw/workspace/projects/polymarket-trading/\n5. Suggest specific integration points where Mirofish could improve the trader (e.g., sentiment analysis, market signals, data enrichment)\n6. Document the integration plan\n\n**Reference:** Was originally part of card_1773793728649 (Install Claude Code tools) but was never actually installed.",
