      "title": "Buy: Biossance Squalane + Marine Algae Eye Cream 15ml",
      "description": "## Product\n**Biossance Squalane + Marine Algae Eye Cream 15ml**\n\n![Product](https://p16-images-sign-sg.tokopedia-static.net/tos-alisg-i-aphluv4xwc-sg/img/VqbcmM/2023/1/3/dccab3f6-0bf3-4509-9b98-b3fee17be4c2.png~tplv-aphluv4xwc-white-pad-v1:1600:1600.jpeg)\n\n- **Price:** Rp1,090,000 (~$68 USD)\n- **Shop:** Beautytrustid (Kab. Tangerang)\n- **Link:** [View on Tokopedia](https://www.tokopedia.com/beautytrust/biossance-squalane-marine-algae-eye-cream)\n- **Cart:** Added\n\n## Seller Trust Analysis\n**VERDICT: HIGH TRUST**\n\n| Metric | Beautytrustid |\n|--------|--------------|\n| Shop rating | 5.0 / 5 |\n| Verified reviews | 3,102 |\n| Total shop sales | 10,000+ |\n| This product sold | 50+ |\n| Product rating | 5.0 / 5 |\n| Price vs retail ($72) | Rp1.09M (~$68) — fair |\n| Seller type | Specialty Western beauty importer |\n| Brands carried | Peach & Lily, Maelove, iS Clinical, Sunday Riley, La Roche Posay, Korres |\n\n## Why Other Listings Were Skipped\nAll 13 other sellers had 0 reviews and 0 sales — typical dropshipper accounts that list products they don't stock. One listing at Rp505K was flagged as fake (15ml retails at ~$72; no legitimate seller offers it at $31).\n\n## Next Step\n- [ ] Complete purchase on Tokopedia\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-23 00:10)\nStill active with 1:58 remaining. Permata Bank sent an OTP code to your registered phone number. I can't access SMS on this machine.\n\n**I need you to check your phone right now** - Permata Bank sent an authentication code (Kode Otentikasi) for the Tokopedia payment of Rp1,147,800. \n\nPlease share the OTP code and I'll enter it immediately. The timer is counting down (~2 minutes left).",
