    {
      "id": "card-mentorships-mc-1774196966769",
      "columnId": "claude-code",
      "title": "Build Mentorships Section + Mission Control Board",
      "description": "## Overview\nBuild a full Mentorships section in Mission Control with client management, payment tracking, session automation, and PDF deliverables.\n\n## 1. Payment & Hour Tracking\n- Track payments through Stripe\n- Auto-pull hours booked from Stripe + manual entry\n- Log time spent per call\n- View showing hours remaining and money paid per client\n\n## 2. Session Management & Automation\n- Dedicated Zoom link for client sessions\n- Monitor for new files in client data folder\n- Grab transcript + cloud recording link when new file appears\n- Save to backend DB and transcripts folder\n- AI summarize session: key points, follow-ups, relevant info → save to client profile\n\n## 3. Centralized Dashboard\n- View all clients and sessions at once\n- Manual entry for sessions (in-person, WhatsApp, etc.)\n- Track client info, tasks, and to-dos\n\n## 4. Client Deliverables\n- After each session, send PDF wrap-up to client\n- Template similar to mastermind PDFs but tailored to mentorship (what happened, key findings, follow-up tasks)\n\n## Extras\n- Pull LinkedIn profiles, websites, and photos for each client when available\n- Eric Horn is the existing example client to reference\n\n## Approach\n- Plan with Opus first, then execute with parallel background agents",
      "order": 0,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-22T16:29:26.769Z",
